'''Livestream's Chatter Banter''' is a [[Relic]] in the set [[Tengoku@Livestream]].

==Description==
[...logging in...]

''HanamiLover4Life'' posted on Aug 10 (Mon) 23:22<br />''■ This is bad! That birthday livestream for Hanami was fake! I wasted my money for nothing! Everyone else got scammed too!''

[Replying to HanamiLover4Life] ''Am I a God'' posted on Aug 10 (Mon) 23:24<br />''■ From what I can gather: Earlier, a hacker uploaded a "RAM Sleep Command" to Hanami's livestream, secretly copying all of Hanami's private data to third-party cloud server nodes without her noticing.''<br />''■ In short, that night, Hanami spent the evening chatting with fake comments, while real viewers were interacting with pre-recorded stream content.''<br />''■ Today, Hanami discovered her money hadn't come through, and realized the hacker had made off with her streaming revenue from two days ago.''

[Replying to Am I a God] ''Tech Guru'' posted on Aug 10 (Mon) 23:28<br />''■ No way, none of the real-time comments showed up? Didn't Hanami notice that all the comments were fake?''

''Voice of 873'' posted on Aug 10 (Mon) 23:33<br />''■ Hanami updated her status: "Nami-nami, I'm so mad! ヽ(ｏ皿′ｏ)ﾉ I've called the police. This is financial fraaaud!"''

[Replying to Tech Guru] ''HanamiLover4Life'' posted on Aug 10 (Mon) 23:36<br />''■ Last time I sent her money, Hanami only said "Thanks for the Super Chat, HanamiLover4Life" and it's the same this time.''<br />''■ How was I supposed to know this was reusing the same response from last time!? I can't tell the difference! I really can't!''<br />''■ Besides, she always ignores non-paying chat messages... I just thought she wasn't paying attention to me.''

''I'm on Fire!'' posted on Aug 10 (Mon) 23:50<br />''■ LMAO, what a cyber heist. Serves her right. Totally deserved.''<br />''■ So many people in the livestream pretending to chat normally, but no one dares to call it out. Everyone thinks that if others don't bring up the issue, then there's no issue.''

[Replying to I'm on Fire!] ''HanamiLover4Life'' posted on Aug 11 (Tue) 00:01<br />''■ I'm done. Never spending money on virtual streamers again.''<br />''■ She never really interacted with me, and I can't tell if she was ever sincere... I thought she would respond in real-time to my live comments, but now I see I was just fooling myself.''

[Replying to HanamiLover4Life] ''Am I a God'' posted on Aug 11 (Tue) 00:15<br />''■ Don't be so negative, bro.''<br />''■ Sure, you got scammed out of your money, but you were happy that day. Does it really matter if that Hanami was real or not?''

''Voice of 873'' posted on Aug 11 (Tue) 00:17<br />''■ Hanami updated her status: "Nami-nami, I can't sleep! Come hang out with me in my livestream~"''

[Replying to Am I a God] ''HanamiLover4Life'' posted on Aug 11 (Tue) 00:18<br />''■ You've got a point there, bro. I'm off to watch the stream.''

[...logging off.]

The livestream countdown begins, as the viewer count climbs steadily. Digital wanderers with mixed emotions stir once again as another wild and sensational broadcast is about to begin...

True feelings mixed with true lies. Truth here ain't worth a dime.

